infrastructureAsCodeIssues.title: Google storage bucket does not use customer-managed keys to encrypt data
infrastructureAsCodeIssues.issue: Google storage bucket does not use customer-managed keys to encrypt data
infrastructureAsCodeIssues.impact: Google will manage the encryption keys on its servers and could access the data without authorization
infrastructureAsCodeIssues.resolve: Use encryption keys from self-managed key management service and configure the `encryption` block accordingly.

remediation.terraform: Use encryption keys from self-managed key management service and configure the `encryption` block accordingly.

iacDescription.issue: Google storage bucket does not use customer-managed keys to encrypt data
iacDescription.impact: Google will manage the encryption keys on its servers and could access the data without authorization
iacDescription.resolve: Use encryption keys from self-managed key management service and configure the `encryption` block accordingly.

infrastructureAsCodeIssues.title: SQL statements may be logged
infrastructureAsCodeIssues.issue: PostgreSQL 'log_min_duration_statement' is not set to -1
infrastructureAsCodeIssues.impact: Some SQL statements may be logged and expose sensitive information
infrastructureAsCodeIssues.resolve: Set the `settings.database_flags.name` attribute to `"log_min_duration_statement"` and `settings.database_flags.value` attribute to `-1`

remediation.terraform: Set the `settings.database_flags.name` attribute to `"log_min_duration_statement"` and `settings.database_flags.value` attribute to `-1`

iacDescription.issue: PostgreSQL 'log_min_duration_statement' is not set to -1
iacDescription.impact: Some SQL statements may be logged and expose sensitive information
iacDescription.resolve: Set the `settings.database_flags.name` attribute to `"log_min_duration_statement"` and `settings.database_flags.value` attribute to `-1`

infrastructureAsCodeIssues.title: Public IP assigned to SQL database instance

infrastructureAsCodeIssues.impact: Database may be accessed remotely over public internet

iacDescription.issue: Public IP will be assigned to the SQL database
iacDescription.impact: Database may be accessed remotely over public internet

infrastructureAsCodeIssues.title: The log_checkpoints is disabled on PostgreSQL DB
infrastructureAsCodeIssues.issue: PostgreSQL 'log_checkpoints' is disabled
infrastructureAsCodeIssues.impact: Verbose logging information of database will not be collected
infrastructureAsCodeIssues.resolve: Set `settings.database_flags.name` attribute to `"log_checkpoints"`, and `settings.database_flags.value` attribute to `"on"`

remediation.terraform: Set `settings.database_flags.name` attribute to `"log_checkpoints"`, and `settings.database_flags.value` attribute to `"on"`

iacDescription.issue: PostgreSQL 'log_checkpoints' is disabled
iacDescription.impact: Verbose logging information of database will not be collected
iacDescription.resolve: Set `settings.database_flags.name` attribute to `"log_checkpoints"`, and `settings.database_flags.value` attribute to `"on"`

infrastructureAsCodeIssues.title: Cloud IAM not configured for CloudSQL instance
infrastructureAsCodeIssues.issue: Cloud IAM not configured for CloudSQL instance
infrastructureAsCodeIssues.impact: Dismissing Cloud IAM makes access control management more difficult and error-prone
infrastructureAsCodeIssues.resolve: Configure a `settings.database_flags` block, with `name` as `cloudsql_iam_authentication` and `value` as `On`

remediation.terraform: Configure a `settings.database_flags` block, with `name` as `cloudsql_iam_authentication` and `value` as `On`

iacDescription.issue: Cloud IAM not configured for CloudSQL instance
iacDescription.impact: Dismissing Cloud IAM makes access control management more difficult and error-prone
iacDescription.resolve: Configure a `settings.database_flags` block, with `name` as `cloudsql_iam_authentication` and `value` as `On`

infrastructureAsCodeIssues.title: Temporary file information is not logged
infrastructureAsCodeIssues.issue: PostgreSQL 'log_temp_files' is not set to 0
infrastructureAsCodeIssues.impact: Some temporary files information may not be logged, which may impact ability to identify potential performance issues
infrastructureAsCodeIssues.resolve: Set the `settings.database_flags.name` attribute to `"log_temp_files"`, and `settings.database_flags.value` attribute to `0`

remediation.terraform: Set the `settings.database_flags.name` attribute to `"log_temp_files"`, and `settings.database_flags.value` attribute to `0`

iacDescription.issue: PostgreSQL 'log_temp_files' is not set to 0
iacDescription.impact: Some temporary files information may not be logged, which may impact ability to identify potential performance issues
iacDescription.resolve: Set the `settings.database_flags.name` attribute to `"log_temp_files"`, and `settings.database_flags.value` attribute to `0`
